<li><a href="https://drupal.org/node/2160735">#2160735</a> by Cottser, aspilicious: Add hook_theme_suggestions_alter() - that completes item #1 from the API changes list of <a href="https://drupal.org/node/2004872">[meta] Theme system architecture changes</a>.</li>
